{"tid":1882410,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打有玩開銀器（18）五大訴求決一不可","createTime":"2020-02-16T08:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T05:55:21.000Z","uid":79765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"abdbe005e7fa240d2333e1fe0efddcdb1b259f10","tid":1882410,"uid":79765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:36:40.000Z","msg":"主要討論各大牌子銀器飾物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家搵到自己鍾意嘅銀器<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各牌子羽毛比較圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3op5c5U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3op5c5U.png&h=e8d07324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各牌子大鷹比較圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OLca8Er.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOLca8Er.png&h=d7fb32f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoros 只建議自行前往日本東京本店購買<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OOhnfjC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOOhnfjC.png&h=3ba9a694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKen Kikuchi 香港無代理 可以搵台灣代理買 : Dawn Rise 昇日屋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZfoKdd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZfoKdd.png&h=3d13aa66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTaro Washimi 香港有代理 : Vinavast<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sMb3Kds.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsMb3Kds.png&h=7467be8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLegend 香港有代理 : Dress Code Silver Hong Kong<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4LDx6U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4LDx6U.png&h=c6a1aade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFirst Arrows 香港Take 5有賣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6Jd6r5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6Jd6r5.png&h=05167f1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHorizon Blue Silver Studio 香港有代理 Horizon Blue Silver Studio - Hong Kong &amp; Macau<br />\n同時台灣都有代理 : Zerockstudio<br />\n（有部分巴打反映香港Horizon blue代理為藍店，而訂貨與收貨期大有出入！<br />\n「落訂前話半年到貨，實際收貨期一年」<br />\n建議考慮入手既巴打自行衡量<br />\n<br />\n以上係比較常見牌子 <br />\n銀器牌子眾多 未能盡錄<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有興趣 香港本地有兩間鋪頭 分別係 Vinavast 同 Dress Code Silver Hong Kong.<br />\n呢兩間鋪頭都有代理唔同牌子既銀器 日本同埋西方都有 有興趣可以抽少少時間上去望望<br />\n<br />\n綁輪方法 : <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SwnZOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SwnZOh.png&h=31145c67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3Eg4fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3Eg4fb.png&h=eb0fc749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n皮繩/銀珠/各類琉璃珠 購買地點 : <br />\n基本上淘寶有齊你所需要既野<br />\n深水埗 美藝華空心銀珠<br />\n大南街 有琉璃珠及皮繩<br />\n古布繩 : 百川<br />\n<br />\n咁多位麻煩睇一睇先 有咩唔明再問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打有意見/有野想加 呢個頭POST可以再改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(credit to 膠膠膠膠巴)<br />\n歡迎各位放自己果Set銀器上黎 交流交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9ba1db3b0c7016741240ffbd642c3cd64c5eae","tid":1882410,"uid":79765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"推。繼續討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed0a978db19916e1a7d25bbbbcf37728a4226a3","tid":1882410,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:38:17.000Z","msg":"(借位thx) 請各位開發新戰線 : Youtube<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目的: 利用youtube演算法, 增加黃絲channel及文宣曝光機會, 降低藍絲文宣的散播速度, 應對中共KOL 100計劃<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲channel&rarr; like、comment、subscribe、share</span><br />\n藍絲channel&rarr; 不感興趣 /不要推薦這個頻道、開1.2秒close(降低續看率)<br />\n<ins>進一步措施</ins> : 利用家中長輩ac dislike + report藍片 &amp;<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 觀看+like黃片</span> (提高黃片在其年齡層的曝光度)<br />\n<br />\n<span style